@startuml EnrollmentLifecycleStateChart
title Enrollment request — state machine

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  BorderColor #333333
}

' Initial creation of a row for (user, course).
[*] --> Pending : submit request\n(new enrollment)

' Administrator decisions (only from Pending).
Pending --> Approved : approve\n[capacity available]
Pending --> Rejected : reject
Pending --> Cancelled : cancel\n(student or admin)

' Student may leave an approved seat.
Approved --> Cancelled : cancel\n(student or admin)

' After rejection or cancellation, a new request\nreopens the same row as Pending.
Rejected --> Pending : request again
Cancelled --> Pending : request again

note bottom of Pending
  **Approve** and **reject** apply only while status is **Pending**.
  **Cancel** is allowed for **Pending** or **Approved**.
end note

@enduml
